  description: 'Decor and Accessories',
  message:
   '“Mia takes your own personality and taste into account and works with what she has at her disposal. She is an angel and an asset to anyone who wants to bring some fresh ideas into their home. Thank you very much Mia for what you have meant to me! Looking forward to working together again.”',
